    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Project ideas</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/sanskrit/misc-software/projects/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/sanskrit/misc-software/projects/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;intro&#34;&gt;Intro&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;People periodically enquire: &amp;ldquo;Request someone to guide me on: What I have to learn and what I can contribute.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Most such people end up contributing nothing despite getting fair project ideas. But some do!&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;We hope some of those will &lt;strong&gt;contribute and share&lt;/strong&gt; good &lt;strong&gt;open source code&lt;/strong&gt; (perfection not required, WIP is fine).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;This page seeks to address such enquiries more concisely.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;contribute-to-existing-open-source-projects&#34;&gt;Contribute to existing open source projects&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;first-find-a-project--team-which-fits-you&#34;&gt;First find a project / team which fits you.&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Click around this site, find useful tools and ideas. Then find out where the source code is published.&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Contribute to this site while at it: &amp;ldquo;Please fix by clicking on the pencil icon and sending a pull request as and when you find errors.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Visit some github organizations and users directly, look at their repositories.&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;An incomplete list, feel free to submit more:&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/sanskrit-coders&#34;&gt;sanskrit-coders&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/sanskrit&#34;&gt;sanskrit&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/indic-dict&#34;&gt;indic-dict&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/drdhaval2785/&#34;&gt;dhaval&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ashtadhyayi&#34;&gt;ashtadhyayi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/kmadathil/sanskrit_parser&#34;&gt;kmadathil&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/shreevatsa&#34;&gt;shreevatsa&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/kmadathil/vvasuki&#34;&gt;vishvas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Look at &lt;a href=&#34;https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/sanskrit-programmers&#34;&gt;mailing list announcements&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Look at the project lists below.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;then-contribute&#34;&gt;Then contribute&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Read some of the source code, contact authors for ideas about how to contribute. Send pull requests, open github issues, sent emails on our mailing list.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;project-idea-lists&#34;&gt;Project idea lists&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://trello.com/b/IRSpxN0b&#34;&gt;Sanskrit coding works trello board&lt;/a&gt; maintained by &lt;a href=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/&#34;&gt;vishvas&lt;/a&gt; - you may contact him in case you want to add projects or find out more about something listed there.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://trello.com/b/VpnAmaBd&#34;&gt;Sanskrit related publishing goals board&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://sanskrit.github.io/groups/dyuganga/&#34;&gt;dyugangA work group&lt;/a&gt; maintained by &lt;a href=&#34;https://vishvAsa.github.io/&#34;&gt;vishvas&lt;/a&gt;. Some of the dictionary/ text/ audio/ video publication and curation projects there require scripting/ scraping and the like. You may contact him in case you want to add projects or find out more about something listed there.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
